(18651, 1, '@NAWACITAPOST1', 'Tanpa Tanda Tangan Presiden Joko Widodo, UU RUU Cipta Kerja ‘Sah’ https://nawacitapost.com/nasional/2020/10/19/tanpa-tanda-tangan-presiden-joko-widodo-uu-ruu-cipta-kerja-sah/…', 'tanda tangan presiden joko widodo undang undang rancang undang undang cipta kerja sah', '0'),
